PRIORITY high
PR REVIEW PROTOCOL
Full pull request review using code-review-graph for token-efficient analysis. 
PRE-REVIEW SETUP
CODE bash 74CHARS
REVIEW STEPS
Get PR context — get_minimal_context(task="PR #[number]: [title]") Check impact — detect_changes() — read RSs Spot broken callers — query_graph(target="[changed function]") Verify tests exist — check test coverage nodes in response Write verdict — use output format below 
PR VERDICT FORMAT
CODE  280CHARS
HARD RULES
Never approve a PR with HIGH risk and no tests Never approve if unrelated files were modified Always check that the PR touches only what the task required (karpathy surgical rule) 